{"tid":8192,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 房有老鼠，嚇到仆街","createTime":"2016-11-28T08:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T10:10:08.000Z","uid":19386,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2314cdadf6993a0cdb767215659864bb129935d3","tid":8192,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，尋晚上上下網突然聽到吱吱聲，勁大隻老鼠唔知點入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚇到企左係床上面，生平最撚驚老鼠。好彩老豆及時趕到，用掃把趕走左。<br />\n<br />\n概念圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbMY2N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbMY2N.jpg&h=6b7dba14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果下次老豆唔係度，我應該點做好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5682363088c11def93e4c3f8f9191d0f53f03ff4","tid":8192,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"你同老鼠講，大叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識你老鼠啊！</span></span>，咁佢聽到知你係熟人，就會走唔打搞你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507cb24208aea6f6abf90dc74348dcd09a7f6f9e","tid":8192,"uid":21453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"巴打住咩屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f124ff06434514b32eda7b9a7c4e7e32deb19664","tid":8192,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"972bf8d5bcbffd4068aaa4685c3210d7551589a8","tid":8192,"uid":12034,"like":0,